snippet: Michelle Wie shot a U.S. Women’s Open course record in the second round, but Na Yeon Choi did her one better the next day on the blustery Blackwolf Run course.
abstract: Na Yeon Choi takes third-round lead at the United States Women’s Open golf tournament.
lead_paragraph: Michelle Wie shot a U.S. Women’s Open course record in the second round, but Na Yeon Choi did her one better the next day on the blustery Blackwolf Run course.

headline.seo: Choi Shoots 65 to Take Lead at U.S. Women’s Open
headline.main: One Player Rises as Wind Replaces Heat at the Open
